					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I'm curious, how do you guys writing games in C keep score? WoW has a score max of 7 digits. which can't really be put nicely into a 16-bit quantity, but works well in a 24 or a 32 bit quantity..am curious if taking this pedestrian route is what's best here, or if somebody knows a more space efficient method?<br /><br />-Thom</div>

